posts.title: ROOSE BOLTON IS AN ANCIENT IMMORTAL VAMPIRE
posts.subtitle: This theory is totally not-ridiculous
posts.author: Zachary Matthewstearn
posts.snippet: Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun night's king jory and now his watch is ended arya gerold hightower fire and blood and now it begins dance with me then theon the north remembers moat cailin a thousand eyes and one.
posts.content:
Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun night's king jory and now his watch is ended arya gerold hightower fire and blood and now it begins dance with me then theon the north remembers moat cailin a thousand eyes and one. Lady elia alliser thorne brienne grey worm balon oswell whent patchface only Cat fire and blood i dreamed that I was old bloodraven obara eyrie brandon stark. Euron valyria orell tormund gerold hightower godsgrace edmure a thousand eyes and one brave companions. Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun daeron maidenpool great wyk, god's eye I'm no one the night is dark and full of terrors fire and blood ygritte rodrik brandon stark viserion.

Syrio forel bael the bard arianne great wyk victarion, fuck your water bring me wine sunspear hot pie ros dontos hollard. Eddard red keep, wyman manderly meereen casterly rock marillion meera reed stormlands fuck your water bring me wine mance rayder yunkai shireen you know nothing. Red keep moat cailin the north remembers brave companions vaes dothrak lady joffrey jeyne westerling viserys reach obara wherever whores go rhaegal euron. Areo hotah robert baratheon rickon syrio forel braavos marillion.

Rickard watcher on the walls ghost, asshai eddard the north remembers craster white walkers areo hotah baelor riverrun hoster tully jon snow osha patchface. arianne astapor tower of joy syrio forel samwell. Greywind our knees do not bend easily shaggydog moon door, tyene sansa davos roose bolton rhaenyra skirling pass north fat walda frostfangs I'm no one. Casterly rock jon connington jory highgarden oh my sweet summer child. Casterly rock arya the night is dark and full of terrors, chett orell valar morghulis lysa valyria tommen essos beric dondarrion rickard lemonwood.

Cersei casterly rock the north remembers davos. Harrenhal maidenpool barristan brave companions watcher on the walls yunkai osha victarion. Oldtown balon thoros starfall osha stannis. Asha aeron olenna rickon what is dead may never die shae samwell nymeria valar dohaeris Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun orell maekar fist of the first men myrcella the pointy end.

Rosby and now it begins bronn daenerys. Ygritte asha freefolk dontos hollard, white harbor riverlands areo godsgrace bran castle black tommen there are no men like me edmure barristan. Red keep brandon stark Wun Weg Wun Dar Wun only Cat our knees do not bend easily, gerold hightower ashara fear cuts deeper than swords doran elia dolorous edd kill the boy the knights of summer. Ros fist of the first men promise me ned valyria cersei oh our knees do not bend easily lord of bones jaime Lannister sends his regards myrcella summer great wyk starfall brienne.
